<concept id="entity_creation_settings">
   <title>Entity creation settings</title>
   <shortdesc />
   <conbody>
      <p>New entities are created on the <xref href="https://help.bricsys.com/hc/en-us/articles/360006534873-Current-Layer" format="html" scope="external">current layer</xref><!--(needs link)-->, using the
         current entity creation settings:<ul id="ul_yws_zr1_2nb">
            <li><xref href="https://help.bricsys.com/hc/en-us/articles/360006531853-Entity-Color" format="html" scope="external">Color</xref><!-- (needs link)--></li>
            <li><xref href="https://help.bricsys.com/hc/en-us/articles/360006534813-Entity-Linetype" format="html" scope="external">Linetype</xref><!-- (needs link)--></li>
            <li><xref href="https://help.bricsys.com/hc/en-us/articles/360006534813-Entity-Linetype#setting-the-global-linetype-scale" format="html" scope="external">Linetype Scale</xref><!-- (needs link)--></li>
            <li><xref href="https://help.bricsys.com/hc/en-us/articles/360006430474-Lineweight" format="html" scope="external">Lineweight</xref><!-- (needs link)--></li>
            <li><xref href="https://help.bricsys.com/hc/en-us/articles/360006535013-Transparency" format="html" scope="external">Transparency</xref><!-- (needs link)--></li>
         </ul></p>
      <p>You can define entity creation settings in the <uicontrol>General</uicontrol> section of
         the <xref keyref="PNL_properties" />.</p>
      <p>You can define all entity creation settings <uicontrol>ByLayer</uicontrol>. This means that the corresponding setting of the current layer is used.</p>
      <p>You can define layer properties in the <xref href="https://help.bricsys.com/hc/en-us/articles/360006704813" format="html" scope="external">Layer</xref><!-- (needs link)--> section in the <xref href="https://help.bricsys.com/hc/en-us/articles/360006807833-Drawing-Explorer" format="html" scope="external">Drawing Explorer</xref><!-- (needs link)--> dialog
         box.</p>
   </conbody>
</concept>
